# requirements: buffered_axi_lite_uart
# extracted from: BALU-RS-001.docx
# extraction date: 2026-04-07
# mode: campaign
# NOTE: Never overwritten by pssgen.
# NOTE: Verification methods pre-populated from VCRM.
